# PHP `app/` conventions

## Namespace ↔ path

`App\Actions\Transactions\Foo` → `app/Actions/Transactions/Foo.php`

After moving controllers/requests, update: class namespace, `routes/*.php`, Pest tests, Pint.

## HTTP symmetry

Match sibling domains:

- `Http/Controllers/Transactions/` (not `Transaction/`)
- `Http/Requests/Accounts/StoreAccountRequest.php` (not loose files in `Requests/` root)

Import HTTP: `Http/Controllers/Imports/`, not under `Transactions/`.

## Actions

```php
// ✅ Action returns models or Data DTO
public function handle(User $user, TransactionIndexFilters $filters): TransactionIndexResult

// ❌ Action formats for Inertia
return (new TransactionResource($transaction))->resolve();
```

Map collections in the controller with `Http/Resources/{Domain}/*`.

## New integrations

Typesense and similar → `app/Integrations/`, register bindings in `AppServiceProvider`.

## Tests

Move tests with code: `tests/Feature/{Domain}/`, `tests/Unit/Data/` or `tests/Unit/Support/{Domain}/`.
